{
  "stem": "868.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As soon as it started moving, the entire compartment got up and applauded us, all the Italians.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They came and embraced us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was one lady there who had a basket of food covered with her clothes, a checkered cloth.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She insisted on giving us all this food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mention this because the contrasts of the average Italian citizen as compared to the French was shocking.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We never encountered such empathy in, in France.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now mind you, I was steeped in the French tradition of liberte, egalite, fraternite.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And France had a long democratic tradition.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the shock was to see how they turned around and collaborated with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't want to imply that all of them did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Of course, there was an underground, the Maquis, which you may have heard, that was very active.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But the average French citizen never showed us such empathy, even those that we knew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Whereas here, suddenly out of nowhere these people, whom we hadn't exchanged two words with, who had only sensed the danger we were in without knowing what was happening-- was a marvelous experience, which I continued then to witness all throughout my stay in Italy.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We made it to Florence and went immediately to the archdiocese, where we were met by the organizers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "In charge of our group was a priest, [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Don Kazeeni ?], [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Don Leto Kazeeni ?], who immediately organized for the women to be hidden in a convent [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in a part of Florence called [?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Vera ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Longo. ?] So my mother and some other women that were in our group were hidden there.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
